      "site.aa99c96550fe30be72": "Data Interpreter",
      "site.8fed4bfdcc738655ef": "Data Interpreter AI Learning Mode is a focused way to use AI for learning instead of passive answer collection. The mode is built around a specific job: Paste data, chart descriptions, or results and learn what they mean, what they do not mean, and what to ask next.",
      "site.a5dea0c193ba1911eb": "Data Interpreter AI Learning Mode: practical guide",
      "site.e843b985180ece286b": "Data Interpreter prompts and study loop",
      "site.8fa05b52a539328a56": "Dates and summaries matter, but learners often need a way into the human situation: what people believed, what choices they saw, what limits shaped them, and what they could not have known.",
      "site.34f0987ebea74fc940": "Debate a claim",
      "site.5ad2a73bcd183978dc": "Debate ambition with Steve Jobs",
      "site.ce821524650cd8b9ee": "debate any topic",
      "site.62563ae4f4175234eb": "Debate any topic",
      "site.262bb159f5f4e6a237": "debate any topic AI",
      "site.f5b58535fe673c4d55": "Debate any topic prompts and study loop",
      "site.907666477e5fe34f49": "Debate any topic, get challenged, compare claims, and learn how to make stronger arguments.",
      "site.1ad54cd1308e88bef2": "Debate causes and consequences",
      "site.fcb57bd2366e2e42cd": "Debate climate policy with Greta Thunberg",
      "site.1034eb0dcf6fc1230d": "Debate helps you separate claims, evidence, values, and assumptions, which makes historical interpretation more precise.",
      "site.75316ab8d0d7f1ec70": "Debate justice with Batman",
      "site.356a459f50ae6007b3": "Debate modes that help learners make claims, face counterarguments, and improve reasoning under pressure.",
      "site.e1a4fa573c7f545d3c": "Debate the claim",
      "site.b1bb71c713289fd31b": "Debate the claim from more than one side so you can notice assumptions, tradeoffs, and weak evidence.",
      "site.4c22a785282a7a33db": "Debate this historical or philosophical claim from both sides. Separate evidence, assumptions, and values.",
      "site.a439a5902a7564d477": "Debate through a chosen voice",
      "site.75e3b09256a062714e": "Debate with a personality",
      "site.3cb0dc27d87c29c430": "Debate with a personality prompts and study loop",
      "site.12822cfbdbe9b42376": "Debate With A Personality Using AI",
      "site.b881756d9e8784dbae": "Debate With A Personality Using AI is a focused way to use AI for learning instead of passive answer collection. The mode is built around a specific job: Name a real or fictional personality and debate them on any topic. The AI channels their public style and worldview while keeping the debate fair.",
      "site.148ea8b187f87b6373": "Debate With A Personality Using AI: practical guide",
