      "site.930075ed955b3c40bc": "Flashcards are one of the simplest ways to do this.",
      "site.417ef8e018cc5949dd": "Flashcards are powerful, but they are not the whole study process. They are best for retrieval, vocabulary, definitions, formulas, distinctions, and key examples. They are weaker when the learner has never understood the idea in the first place.",
      "site.4717d13b6ef8aea9d2": "Flashcards work best when they test one idea at a time, reveal answers only after effort, and review missed cards sooner.",
