      "site.40e2c08da2160a0ea3": "Information is everywhere. Understanding is still unevenly distributed.",
      "site.310100649b9dc0e375": "Inside the live mode, the core job is: {value1}. That focus keeps the session pointed at progress instead of another long explanation.",
      "site.f1897f08369e9e129a": "Inside the live mode, the goal is to turn a vague question into a focused session with examples, checks, and a useful next action.",
