      "site.8376be205682ee6d73": "inspir school AI learning use cases",
      "site.22a0185bd923ac526a": "inspir school deployment features",
      "site.0375a80118aee62f24": "inspir school deployment path",
      "site.f22a70cdfef34c2c3d": "inspir separates free guest learning from saved personal conversations, so learners, families, and schools know what is public and what stays private.",
      "site.89faa73d9dd280935c": "inspir started as a Facebook page publishing quizzes and building a habit of extracurricular learning.",
      "site.c319db7864f4a2a416": "inspir story reference links",
      "site.3c484375115c596761": "inspir story timeline",
      "site.99d8f44c47a09c1c47": "inspir treats AI as an enabler, not the mission itself. The mission is better access to learning: clearer explanations, more practice, stronger curiosity, and a future where every child can reach a capable tutor for free or very low cost.",
      "site.4ac2909a95b5cb3155": "inspir trust principles",
      "site.1112a96675c333239f": "inspir trust reference links",
      "site.0122c1283c1bf98b16": "inspir turns curiosity, homework, revision, and big questions into guided AI learning sessions that explain, ask back, and help you practise.",
      "site.6f9bb15d5656ddcd31": "Inspir wants to help in ensuring learning should be fun and for everyone. We strive for a day education reaches to everyone, everywhere through technology. Starting with the 1,415,422,077 in India.",
      "site.9a918550bd051e01ee": "inspir went live as a consumer-facing AI learning product within weeks of ChatGPT's public release.",
      "site.c95704db98e681e01f": "inspir works with schools to offer tailored AI chat experiences for students, built around confidentiality, curriculum needs, and the practical realities of school deployment.",
      "site.6f70af069c7834e22c": "inspir: You can Learn Anything",
      "site.71cfe5d0d8c29009a6": "inspir.uk next-generation buildout",
      "site.e4a80a99ebbb651c60": "inspir's Flashcard Builder is designed around that active recall loop: build a deck, try the front, reveal the answer, rate your recall, and review the misses until the idea sticks.",
      "site.d917b76739de3f275c": "inspir’s go-to-market grew from an existing offline network of schools and universities that had already engaged with extracurricular programmes and student events. That network helped inspir reach more than one million users across the free platform and partner schools.",
      "site.5d6c0f3138da1e91a8": "inspir's mission is to make learning accessible, engaging, enjoyable, and useful for everyone through free public AI learning tools.",
      "site.76e0e32283eeaf309d": "inspir's mission is to make learning accessible, engaging, enjoyable, and useful through free public AI learning tools and school-ready learning spaces.",
      "site.3bd9a50d0e640143be": "inspir's public modes let teachers evaluate the product through real learning flows before considering a school deployment or a tailored classroom pathway.",
      "site.9fbce84dcd4f62749c": "inspir&apos;s work includes retrieval-based learning systems, NCERT content ingestion, structured prompting, custom LLM evaluation, and open-source engagement around RAG evaluation. The current platform lives at inspirlearning.com while the next generation is being built in public through inspir.uk and GitHub.",
      "site.82b5464557e8f95308": "Inspiring individuals to be creative and capable of withstanding the AI revolution is essential. Only by providing essential products and services for free to those who cannot afford them and sustaining access for those who can, can the world pursue happiness collectively.",
      "site.a47c353d55869e468a": "Instead of dropping a long answer, inspir helps you choose a simpler foundation, a deeper route, or a practical example.",
      "site.8936785ba5f3782382": "Intellectual Property",
