      "site.a75d69d88d5b79e866": "No. The comparison links only to public guest-mode entrypoints, guides, prompt libraries, and learning paths. Private saved conversations are not used as source content.",
      "site.aed10f9f91c9bf277a": "No. The comparison pages are written to show when inspir is a better first click for live AI tutoring, prompts, and guest learning modes, and when a structured curriculum or official course library may still be useful.",
      "site.ca986baef0a79e4806": "No. They link only to public pages, public guest modes, guides, prompts, and learning paths. Private saved chats stay private.",
      "site.537fbac462af326c4e": "No. Treat generated dialogue as a learning simulation. Cite real primary or secondary sources for factual claims.",
