      "site.0d39a9ba5b54ac590b": "Public guest modes give anyone a useful place to start, while school and partner deployments can adapt the experience for local needs.",
      "site.9e27eb71ffaf2c0d95": "Public guest-mode links exist so learners can start directly in useful learning modes from search, social links, schools, or shared recommendations.",
