      "site.8479e8174d72f35dd6": "Talk To Historical Figures With AI",
      "site.fd491be7a558f38bc7": "Talk To Historical Figures With AI is a focused way to use AI for learning instead of passive answer collection. The mode is built around a specific job: Step into conversation with a historical figure. Ask questions, challenge ideas, and hear the world through their era, values, and limits.",
      "site.3183f69986b7ceed7c": "Talk To Historical Figures With AI: practical guide",
