      "site.5538da70a45fdebd14": "Teach vocabulary through context and retrieval practice.",
      "site.f2604f9b72ad42b1d5": "Teachers",
      "site.593b16049d757719a6": "Teachers and leaders can start with Learn Anything, Socratic Instruction, Homework Coach, quizzes, and flashcards before a formal rollout.",
      "site.bda68a0e93312745da": "Teachers need more than a generic chatbot. They need predictable learning behaviors: ask questions, check reasoning, generate practice, preserve student voice, and make misconceptions visible.",
      "site.ece53407c8b8eb8957": "Teachers or parents evaluating focused AI learning behaviors before a school deployment.",
      "site.02cb46a174d057cb83": "Technical story",
      "site.eb1a9c43e5e238e0b6": "Tell a scene, pause for prediction or reflection, and connect back to the concept.",
      "site.7d1142e4547e426c6b": "Tell the mode what you are trying to learn or produce.",
