      "site.cf4115b05ed51aeb4f": "This matters for schools and families because the first barrier is often not talent. It is the cost of help, the fear of asking a \"basic\" question, or the lack of a patient person at the exact moment confusion appears. A free public companion lowers the cost of beginning.",
