      "site.f16c6e97bad511c06f": "Use Writing Coach to turn the argument into clearer structure.",
      "site.3fb5408e7457bf73c1": "Use Writing Coach when this is the right mode for the job. If you want a related path, try Science Lab Partner. You can also browse the AI learning blog for study methods, Socratic learning, flashcards, roleplay, and active recall.",
      "site.74c889d60e73579cf5": "Use Writing Coach when you want a session that starts quickly but still adapts to you. The first goal is not to sound impressive. The first goal is to make the next step feel possible.",
      "site.cedb4e92bf7b0e0fcc": "Use writing feedback for structure, clarity, and evidence while keeping the final draft recognizably yours.",
      "site.babb6412809e8916fc": "Useful AI learning has a clear contract.",
      "site.22ae52c971e1606ead": "Useful from the first click",
      "site.417b0db3c3e321bdae": "Useful reference points for coverage and partners.",
      "site.272f9a3e858e31920c": "Useful subject help ends with proof that the idea stuck.",
      "site.e3fe6cbb44e8f7e1e0": "Validate the feeling, identify the blocker, and choose one small next step.",
      "site.754f12f4e5a90a1566": "Verify important facts with trusted sources, textbooks, or teacher-provided materials.",
