      "site.dcdcefcef74b939582": "Vocabulary Builder",
      "site.19637f7cace496a827": "Vocabulary Builder AI Learning Mode is a focused way to use AI for learning instead of passive answer collection. The mode is built around a specific job: Build vocabulary with meaning, examples, pronunciation cues, memory hooks, and quick practice.",
