      "site.43ec5c5a05b4954ea6": "Active practice",
      "site.8bc4fbc90c8e9c86b6": "Active recall review",
      "site.f68f1f0ca7c2e9bea4": "After each hint, explain why the step works before continuing.",
      "site.8a46d135cf50f178dc": "After the simulation, summarize the setting, constraints, and evidence.",
