      "site.5223abcc7a10e74cff": "Test your reasoning",
      "site.27ab1313ce5cd637c8": "The blog connects useful learning advice to live practice, so a guide can become a study session in one step.",
      "site.2612682890bf429128": "The blog is organized around real study moments: getting unstuck, remembering more, writing better, preparing for exams, and exploring ideas with a patient tutor.",
      "site.d9c636955d36e0ee3a": "The broader open-source inspir platform.",
      "site.059c79ee431bfc4427": "The closing beat returns to the mission: public access, schools, and a more open way to learn.",
      "site.9c2dd1d68f53e68960": "The current inspirlearning.com rebuild.",
      "site.e92b2222fa496b32ce": "The film shifts from inspiration into the practical promise: a patient AI learning companion.",
      "site.7e6ed2d38c989652c5": "The homework and Socratic modes are designed around hints, reasoning, step checks, and learner explanations instead of simply handing over finished answers.",
      "site.58be6769f6599885a2": "The middle section frames inspir around understanding, hints, quizzes, and active learning loops.",
      "site.6bc1b280c55aceeb1b": "The next-generation AI study platform.",
      "site.59b5ab693533b9d350": "The opening frames set up learning as something anyone should be able to start immediately.",
      "site.33237ba4c491cb9422": "The public site is structured like a learning map: live modes for immediate help, subject hubs for learner questions, and guides that turn reading into action.",
      "site.09ad4dd2ea0c36ebb3": "The site is a route, not a brochure.",
      "site.f875dfe94a0d5ef0d2": "Think deeper",
      "site.534f9712426325b6e2": "Time travel",
      "site.e380cdbfb5a190fcaf": "Topic clusters",
