      "site.3c484375115c596761": "inspir story timeline",
      "site.99d8f44c47a09c1c47": "inspir treats AI as an enabler, not the mission itself. The mission is better access to learning: clearer explanations, more practice, stronger curiosity, and a future where every child can reach a capable tutor for free or very low cost.",
      "site.9a918550bd051e01ee": "inspir went live as a consumer-facing AI learning product within weeks of ChatGPT's public release.",
