      "site.06c23cd9959a36b98c": "A useful card asks one thing. It should not hide five questions inside one prompt. It should be specific enough to answer, but not so narrow that it becomes meaningless.",
      "site.938617f5429d417dd6": "A useful historical AI response should have two layers.",
      "site.c2751a7d7252649785": "A weak AI flashcard says:",
      "site.f1449165e307d51868": "A weak prompt only names a topic. A strong prompt names the topic, the level, the sticking point, and the kind of help you want. Use this {value1} as the context, then ask the mode to make you do something with it.",
