      "site.48f8fdfa47c42f289d": "AI critical thinking tutor",
      "site.729d4425bdaaf80f4e": "AI debate coach",
      "site.2598763f61ea6b6bb6": "AI Debate Coach For Sharper Arguments is a focused way to use AI for learning instead of passive answer collection. The mode is built around a specific job: Pick any topic and go head-to-head in a real debate. Choose a side, get challenged, and learn to make better arguments.",
      "site.8859b800f7eee19699": "AI Debate Coach For Sharper Arguments: practical guide",
      "site.31d2d79f22f9a1f3a5": "AI debate practice",
      "site.e6359b6c064a0101f4": "AI exam planner",
      "site.bf462c9796fffadf77": "AI Exam Prep Planner For Realistic Study Schedules is a focused way to use AI for learning instead of passive answer collection. The mode is built around a specific job: Build a realistic exam plan from your date, syllabus, strengths, and weak areas.",
      "site.774db7d70706801265": "AI Exam Prep Planner Study Schedule Guide",
      "site.5a49a5d3cb6e13e70d": "AI Flashcard Builder For Active Recall is a focused way to use AI for learning instead of passive answer collection. The mode is built around a specific job: Turn notes or topics into clear flashcards with answers, traps, and review prompts.",
