      "site.863e8e7d7988c74d88": "AI historical conversation can help when it is handled carefully.",
      "site.b304cc7b41fd7f5598": "AI history tutor",
      "site.8b3a4d41374e746147": "AI Homework Coach With Hints, Not Answer Dumping is a focused way to use AI for learning instead of passive answer collection. The mode is built around a specific job: Get unstuck on homework with hints, examples, and checks that help you do the thinking yourself.",
      "site.9c3d823515756d4b46": "AI Homework Coach With Hints, Not Answer Dumping: practical guide",
