      "site.e843b985180ece286b": "Data Interpreter prompts and study loop",
      "site.8fa05b52a539328a56": "Dates and summaries matter, but learners often need a way into the human situation: what people believed, what choices they saw, what limits shaped them, and what they could not have known.",
