      "site.b881756d9e8784dbae": "Debate With A Personality Using AI is a focused way to use AI for learning instead of passive answer collection. The mode is built around a specific job: Name a real or fictional personality and debate them on any topic. The AI channels their public style and worldview while keeping the debate fair.",
      "site.148ea8b187f87b6373": "Debate With A Personality Using AI: practical guide",
