      "site.8bbc7accade6d600ca": "Did you answer at least one question before reading the correction?",
      "site.210a67f212873c98b8": "Different learning jobs need different flows. Use a homework coach for hints, a math step coach for problem solving, a Socratic tutor for deep understanding, flashcards for recall, and quizzes for pressure-tested practice.",
