      "site.e432ca14e7c051fcc6": "Feynman Tutor",
      "site.76506817436f2576b3": "Feynman Tutor AI Learning Mode is a focused way to use AI for learning instead of passive answer collection. The mode is built around a specific job: Try explaining a concept simply. Your tutor spots gaps, asks questions, and helps you rebuild the explanation.",
