      "site.f7f5b73308cbcca473": "Finish by writing a five-bullet recap from memory, then ask for the one weak spot to review tomorrow.",
      "site.88f39658d8034604e0": "Finish by writing the idea back from memory.",
      "site.45f58c9b7eb5c3a913": "Finish with a quiz, flashcard, or Socratic check so the session leaves a trace.",
      "site.239a1681ee458f631a": "First, the tutor identifies the target. \"I want to understand opportunity cost\" is different from \"I need to solve this economics homework question\" or \"I need to defend a position in debate.\" The target shapes the questions.",
      "site.3c22f541142cb4ab5b": "Fix the misconception.",
      "site.8d3383856ae937dbc8": "Flashcard Builder",
