      "site.62656f47e151dcabf2": "Reading an AI response is not the same as learning. After the first answer, ask the mode to make you do something with the idea.",
      "site.63ce795b57192cbcf4": "Reading Companion",
      "site.e038052361a204a0f1": "Reading Companion AI Learning Mode is a focused way to use AI for learning instead of passive answer collection. The mode is built around a specific job: Bring a passage or book idea and build comprehension through summaries, vocabulary, inference, and discussion.",
