      "site.8c596b957def911ecc": "Reading Companion prompts and study loop",
      "site.d6b801afe137857e4e": "Reading notes feels productive. Remembering them later is the real test.",
      "site.810fcee272d9478268": "Reading time",
      "site.f435cc551f55cc23c2": "Ready to try the learning modes?",
      "site.eb7a2f0e1b8f586950": "Recall later. Turn the weak spot into a card in Flashcard Builder or a short quiz in Quiz Me On Trivia.",
      "site.8c1e0e4d6d322c1356": "Recommended AI learning guide library",
