      "site.37a21c2b6b0edd6da8": "Research Assistant",
      "site.742a67e2a02c54782d": "Research Assistant AI Learning Mode is a focused way to use AI for learning instead of passive answer collection. The mode is built around a specific job: Turn a broad topic into research questions, search terms, outlines, and source notes.",
