      "site.94553c6cf31bf47994": "Review weak areas.",
      "site.30447373509e7c559f": "Review without looking at the back.",
      "site.10843f8950ff1a37bd": "Revise with a reason.",
      "site.e1860601a25415104f": "Roleplay Scenario",
      "site.93f68ed0e1964ad554": "Roleplay Scenario AI Learning Mode is a focused way to use AI for learning instead of passive answer collection. The mode is built around a specific job: Practice negotiation, conflict, customer support, leadership, or any high-stakes conversation.",
      "site.90cd34f310bfc155ca": "Roleplay Scenario AI Learning Mode: practical guide",
      "site.15bb536ae0b0868eb3": "Roleplay Scenario prompts and study loop",
      "site.050220dc04d444a445": "Routes to continue learning",
      "site.28e8bb837378c5399c": "Save the next review step",
      "site.d8c3070d7f11d6c224": "Say the goal in ordinary language.",
      "site.fc6aaea6992bd9607c": "Schedule quizzes and recall before rereading so the plan reveals weak spots.",
      "site.662605cea1c14c8a36": "Science Lab Partner",
      "site.43b1041c4830b87379": "Science Lab Partner AI Learning Mode is a focused way to use AI for learning instead of passive answer collection. The mode is built around a specific job: Plan safe demonstrations, understand variables, predict outcomes, and reason from evidence like a scientist.",
      "site.6f1f12f0064ba6c964": "Science Lab Partner AI Learning Mode: practical guide",
      "site.e24618ba1b4bd73298": "Science Lab Partner prompts and study loop",
      "site.55e96beff0827173d3": "Second, the tutor asks a diagnostic question. It should be simple enough to answer but revealing enough to expose the learner's current model.",
      "site.3ceefbc0e3ff41b5f9": "See how students can use AI tutoring while keeping the thinking active.",
      "site.059ef2763a2a737271": "Separate in-character claims from evidence notes.",
      "site.63454dca6f69dbeae0": "Set a topic.",
      "site.efd74f909673bee7ae": "Set the scene",
      "site.97dff24e4c5635df97": "Shape the work",
      "site.eb142eede9b957ee66": "Socratic AI",
      "site.02d037850c2cf33c49": "Socratic AI Tutor For Deeper Understanding is a focused way to use AI for learning instead of passive answer collection. The mode is built around a specific job: Turn a concept, argument, problem, text, or decision into a focused chain of questions. Your buddy listens to each answer, maps assumptions and gaps, and pushes you toward your own final synthesis. Try: \"Help me understand opportunity cost.\"",
      "site.943120ea1758e0e62d": "Socratic AI Tutor For Deeper Understanding: practical guide",
      "site.f5087594226914bf70": "Socratic debate AI",
      "site.bfac28b8b6c02e7484": "Socratic Instruction",
      "site.4737a87f633bdcbfe4": "Socratic Instruction prompts and study loop",
      "site.6b301fd9e1520bf0c0": "Socratic learning",
      "site.88f15ed7c65ba44840": "Socratic tutoring is not always the answer. If a learner has no background at all, a short explanation may be kinder than a question. If they are in crisis before a deadline, a planning mode like Exam Prep Planner or a hint mode like Homework Coach may be better. If the goal is remembering terms, Flashcard Builder is more direct.",
      "site.50de465a2e853df96b": "Socratic tutoring uses questions, hypotheses, hints, and reflection to build deeper understanding than passive answer reading.",
      "site.0c077975b330bed917": "Source Critic",
      "site.fcc0e6f05943dc97f4": "Source Critic AI Learning Mode is a focused way to use AI for learning instead of passive answer collection. The mode is built around a specific job: Evaluate articles, claims, videos, or posts for evidence, bias, reliability, and missing context.",
      "site.a921df9cd99648655c": "Source Critic AI Learning Mode: practical guide",
      "site.38cc491120ed790edd": "Source Critic prompts and study loop",
      "site.3f28819ab7fad425a3": "Spaced Review",
      "site.61a314e6c982c305c8": "Spaced Review AI Learning Mode is a focused way to use AI for learning instead of passive answer collection. The mode is built around a specific job: Plan and run quick review sessions that strengthen long-term memory.",
      "site.36042eb1224372c863": "Spaced Review AI Learning Mode: practical guide",
      "site.3ecedd62e60b19e7a7": "Spaced Review prompts and study loop",
      "site.d1b60eb3470f607df4": "Speaking Practice",
      "site.ef0f44ba3f77ce66dc": "Speaking Practice AI Learning Mode is a focused way to use AI for learning instead of passive answer collection. The mode is built around a specific job: Prepare speeches, presentations, interviews, or oral exams with prompts, timing, and feedback on structure.",
      "site.644c4a4f387f0f121a": "Speaking Practice AI Learning Mode: practical guide",
