      "site.cd4070756edded8a69": "Use Vocabulary Builder when you want a session that starts quickly but still adapts to you. The first goal is not to sound impressive. The first goal is to make the next step feel possible.",
      "site.5c00c1229119b40914": "Use Writing Coach for structure, clarity, evidence, and revision priorities.",
      "site.c031d260c0f9746360": "Use Writing Coach to improve structure, clarity, and voice.",
      "site.f16c6e97bad511c06f": "Use Writing Coach to turn the argument into clearer structure.",
      "site.3fb5408e7457bf73c1": "Use Writing Coach when this is the right mode for the job. If you want a related path, try Science Lab Partner. You can also browse the AI learning blog for study methods, Socratic learning, flashcards, roleplay, and active recall.",
      "site.74c889d60e73579cf5": "Use Writing Coach when you want a session that starts quickly but still adapts to you. The first goal is not to sound impressive. The first goal is to make the next step feel possible.",
      "site.754f12f4e5a90a1566": "Verify important facts with trusted sources, textbooks, or teacher-provided materials.",
      "site.dc97c84513daa310ff": "View modes",
      "site.2365f31a23b256dde0": "Viva Practice",
      "site.9bb9921e99ff1e258d": "Viva Practice AI Learning Mode is a focused way to use AI for learning instead of passive answer collection. The mode is built around a specific job: Practice viva, oral exams, project defenses, and rapid follow-up questions with calm feedback.",
      "site.c4255e0bb155f796af": "Viva Practice AI Learning Mode: practical guide",
      "site.40d5123891b796f2de": "Viva Practice prompts and study loop",
      "site.dcdcefcef74b939582": "Vocabulary Builder",
      "site.19637f7cace496a827": "Vocabulary Builder AI Learning Mode is a focused way to use AI for learning instead of passive answer collection. The mode is built around a specific job: Build vocabulary with meaning, examples, pronunciation cues, memory hooks, and quick practice.",
      "site.afd2aa4628a25e2ad6": "Vocabulary Builder AI Learning Mode: practical guide",
