      "site.f4877740cc39cf8b66": "What the companion should provide",
      "site.231fbf27878f2698ea": "What this mode helps with",
      "site.a29b4b5ee632ee4d44": "What to ask a historical figure",
      "site.5d87e0b2c178c83a36": "What would change your mind?",
      "site.3ab45d2d5936f0cebc": "What would modern readers misunderstand?",
      "site.7a06aa5005af39b273": "When {value1} is the right next step",
      "site.23ed22107e266940e1": "When Socratic tutoring is the wrong tool",
      "site.90c45801d6b2f1d37a": "When you paste notes into AI, ask it to split broad ideas into those jobs. A deck with 18 specific cards is usually better than a deck with 5 giant cards that each contain a whole paragraph.",
      "site.4335b162337ad74d7f": "Where AI can help",
