      "site.c6a0698369a8945180": "{value1} related guides",
      "site.65900c36a88f60e657": "A course library is strongest when the search query matches a known skill, topic, or standard.",
      "site.edabc431ff514b9c5d": "A Khan Academy alternative for live AI learning moments.",
      "site.ef781ca91cb18dafd8": "A learner choosing between tools usually needs one of three things: a structured curriculum, a live tutor for the stuck point, or a practice loop that makes the idea stay learned.",
      "site.70936515d0fddcd33c": "A learner often moves through prepared videos, articles, exercises, and dashboards.",
      "site.fa833204940c724775": "A learner starts inside a mode-specific chat and can ask for a simpler model, a harder question, a quiz, a flashcard deck, or a critique.",
      "site.99f629cd17925bf58d": "AI homework coach alternative",
