      "site.df07ec19847b7e3c81": "Choose the right learning tool for the moment.",
      "site.f07ac22a9e938c6666": "Common questions",
      "site.8d105cf44d3926289e": "Compare",
      "site.fe86b8b6f58d6b02ba": "Compare inspir with other learning tools and choose when to use live AI tutoring, public guest modes, prompts, guides, and study workflows.",
      "site.2dfcf898a3bd4e0111": "Comparison",
      "site.e3449bc43c80fff108": "Comparison FAQ",
      "site.0fbba3305ce0419e5b": "comparison page",
      "site.23364909eb300169f1": "Curriculum",
      "site.e5d9412dc19e3b731b": "Do not ask which product wins. Ask which learning behavior fits.",
      "site.de89ad80e4bc159305": "Do the comparison pages include private user chats?",
      "site.f52c663e3e94fc11d1": "Does this comparison include private user chats?",
      "site.b054bfce39dfee30f5": "Each comparison is written to be fair, useful, and action-oriented: what the known tool is good for, where inspir is different, and which public mode to open first.",
      "site.062d9fa39541732fef": "Each page links the comparison to live modes, guides, prompts, and practical study paths.",
      "site.20a6d39875c4552e6d": "Every link here opens public learning material. Private user chats stay private.",
      "site.c48d44e9c6efbb98fa": "External facts are linked to official sources.",
      "site.e0a9a4669618e9e8d1": "Fair comparisons help learners choose faster.",
      "site.dab564d8093c751818": "Fit",
