      "site.1f2797f9270f64d421": "Homework Coach and Math Step Coach are tuned for hint-first support, step checks, and ownership of the final answer.",
      "site.e67051684a0a7efe2e": "How to combine them",
      "site.55680701f00ceb9366": "How to compare",
