      "site.dbe2f41ef4ff955e5b": "I want history to feel alive but still evidence-aware.",
      "site.e6cf030a4409f4caf0": "I watched a lesson but still do not get it.",
      "site.b799727ddea54cfad2": "inspir comparison pages should be useful without pretending another platform is static. Check official sources for the latest product details.",
      "site.0fb7f30ad6ff523377": "inspir is built around public guest AI modes: Socratic questions, homework hints, math steps, writing feedback, quizzes, flashcards, and study planning.",
      "site.21037e55b97f4451ae": "Interaction style",
      "site.919776a2ca87b87d66": "Is inspir a replacement for Khan Academy?",
      "site.299b9447921e060357": "Khan Academy",
