      "site.d6159273dec809735b": "Open workflow",
      "site.6fac9f52368e39d91f": "Parents are often trying to help without taking over. inspir gives families public modes that make learning behavior visible: hints, questions, explain-back, review, and study planning.",
      "site.f472423dd7ed509f76": "Paste the question, what you tried, and the stuck point. Ask for the smallest useful hint, not the final answer.",
