      "site.3e939374690504dfaa": "Use Study Plan Builder or Habit Coach to make small sessions and restarts visible.",
      "site.a93d795818eef68115": "Use Study Plan Builder to choose a small goal, then use quizzes, flashcards, project steps, or concept maps to prove progress.",
      "site.2e70f72096c6eab75b": "Use the school page to explore custom workflows, confidentiality needs, and rollout steps.",
      "site.5d9bb768150af8e301": "Use Writing Coach for feedback on structure, clarity, evidence, and revision priorities.",
      "site.babb6412809e8916fc": "Useful AI learning has a clear contract.",
