      "site.62563ae4f4175234eb": "Debate any topic",
      "site.fcb57bd2366e2e42cd": "Debate climate policy with Greta Thunberg",
      "site.1034eb0dcf6fc1230d": "Debate helps you separate claims, evidence, values, and assumptions, which makes historical interpretation more precise.",
      "site.75316ab8d0d7f1ec70": "Debate justice with Batman",
      "site.e1a4fa573c7f545d3c": "Debate the claim",
      "site.b1bb71c713289fd31b": "Debate the claim from more than one side so you can notice assumptions, tradeoffs, and weak evidence.",
      "site.4c22a785282a7a33db": "Debate this historical or philosophical claim from both sides. Separate evidence, assumptions, and values.",
      "site.a439a5902a7564d477": "Debate through a chosen voice",
      "site.75e3b09256a062714e": "Debate with a personality",
