      "site.7c25dbf4c80716fe2a": "More than 100 guides, prompt loops, and pillar clusters for AI-assisted learning.",
      "site.727575fe0bff2db9c3": "Move from pilot to wider access through school funding, partner support, or CSR pathways for learners who need subsidised access.",
      "site.709a23220f2c3d64d1": "Name",
