      "site.f6ec33c709aa4ef2c5": "Turn a concept, argument, problem, text, or decision into a focused chain of questions. Your buddy listens to each answer, maps assumptions and gaps, and pushes you toward your own final synthesis. Try: \"Help me understand opportunity cost.\"",
