      "site.0932a94e5d6a298f32": "School deployments can be adapted around custom content, workflows, prompts, and NCERT-aligned learning needs where appropriate.",
      "site.fb8a562ed5a2ef48b1": "School leaders",
      "site.dfcc75effae975f1f2": "School rollouts can be planned around student privacy, staff oversight, and the practical boundaries a learning community needs.",
