      "site.341cd17bedeac35477": "Schools and partners can build from the public product toward tailored, confidential, and subsidized deployments.",
      "site.c64f97bc689af465da": "Schools can evaluate inspir through public guest modes first, then explore tailored AI learning spaces with custom workflows, confidentiality planning, curriculum needs, and funded access paths.",
      "site.43d5179e32da3aee00": "Schools can evaluate public modes first, then discuss tailored workflows, confidentiality planning, content needs, and funded access.",
      "site.e2066562417df70fb3": "Schools can start by trying the public modes, then move toward a tailored version when they need custom workflows, content alignment, or funded access.",
      "site.58d68211fdd6de8ff7": "Schools can test public guest modes first, then use the schools page to explore tailored workflows, confidentiality planning, NCERT-aligned options, and funded access.",
      "site.9af4ab277a3efff0ca": "Search and directory access",
      "site.396c2137a0b503759e": "Short description",
      "site.2f4874f752f6a9e036": "Simple paths from public guest mode to school deployment.",
      "site.b8be87ac79be1e4f67": "Start directly in the right learning mode for homework hints, maths steps, writing critique, quizzes, flashcards, or exam planning.",
      "site.b07d6ad9211653d933": "Start with public guest mode, then shape the school version around real needs.",
      "site.d61c21978811629826": "Structured catalog of public pages, modes, learning paths, blog clusters, and privacy boundaries.",
      "site.14bbe4f2e7e03f99bc": "Student AI chat",
      "site.fcfac3efb6ae696fcb": "Students",
      "site.e801a140bd2cecc961": "Students need direct support, teachers need focused learning behavior, leaders need responsible deployment paths, and partners need clear ways to fund access.",
      "site.a72eb3d150a98b94ed": "Study workflows that connect guest modes, prompts, practice, and related guides.",
      "site.7a26ee15fb4dcef377": "Support funded AI learning access for communities that need high-quality support without adding cost to families.",
      "site.b46d519f5333a0cd38": "Syndicated coverage for wider consumer reach.",
      "site.dd0cb37d21421cc9b5": "Tailored AI learning experiences for school communities, curriculum needs, confidentiality planning, and funded access.",
      "site.f2604f9b72ad42b1d5": "Teachers",
      "site.593b16049d757719a6": "Teachers and leaders can start with Learn Anything, Socratic Instruction, Homework Coach, quizzes, and flashcards before a formal rollout.",
      "site.a55a275aa676930d92": "Terms",
      "site.1948c2f30f9d9a0e3f": "Text-first reference file for assistants, educators, partners, and citation tools.",
      "site.75315bf01cc1885d78": "The app is organized around teaching behaviors such as Socratic questioning, homework hints, quizzes, flashcards, roleplay, and planning.",
      "site.ca06b087a01c80e9bf": "The community expanded through schools, universities, competitions, extracurricular programmes, and learner communities.",
      "site.e696316178c72e9eb7": "The formal privacy page for data use, rights, and public service conditions.",
      "site.880ee7075c5a4ca8d5": "The formal terms covering acceptable use, account responsibilities, and service conditions.",
      "site.d7a6f2caf1c2c8aa63": "The goal is to help people find the right public learning page quickly. Public routes, guides, and learning hubs are open; API, admin, reset, and private utility routes stay closed.",
      "site.42c11babbea60523de": "The live access rules for public and private routes.",
      "site.9d1d9471b315f09acf": "The live learning experience that turns the mission into practical help.",
      "site.cc1cf401efc5eb8129": "The next phase is open-source, contributor-friendly, and connected to the wider international buildout at inspir.uk.",
      "site.28d20a8ac18159f705": "The open-source rebuild for developers, educators, and contributors.",
      "site.7b40bef2257ef20729": "The platform worked on curriculum ingestion, retrieval, structured learning flows, and early AI tutoring experiences.",
      "site.2f43cb98604fb87f4b": "The public blog contains more than 100 guides, prompt loops, and pillar clusters connected to live learning modes.",
      "site.cd1c2df7a40adc8918": "The public explanation of why inspir exists and why learning access matters.",
      "site.69d23cb9bb40280f04": "The public inspir platform helps learners practise extracurricular activities and explore ideas. School deployments can be customised around each school’s content, workflows, and student context.",
      "site.1a560827f6f4063078": "The public modes are designed around learning behavior: hints, Socratic questions, step checks, quizzes, flashcards, writing feedback, review loops, and active explanation.",
      "site.8d9dd466b2bb393181": "The public product is easy to try first, while schools and partners can explore tailored deployments for community needs.",
      "site.8bf78ce7f393aef11b": "The public product keeps learning easy to try, while schools and CSR partners can support tailored deployments when communities need confidentiality, curriculum alignment, or funded access.",
      "site.1156df2895fe03db82": "The public statement of why inspir exists and what learning access means.",
      "site.cea59ef50b530ec865": "The school pathway for tailored AI learning spaces and funded access.",
      "site.1e958c1dbf49c2dc3e": "The story from quizzes and student communities to free AI learning tools built in public.",
      "site.47373de172b1b2a6cb": "The story spans quizzes, offline school networks, curriculum ingestion, and public AI learning modes.",
      "site.500e3a21005f09965c": "The strongest angle is free public AI learning that opens directly in guest mode and keeps learners active through mode-specific teaching rather than generic answer generation.",
      "site.d0f882b17719ce7412": "The wider international buildout connected to the inspir project.",
      "site.510b1bc750f44afe6c": "The written learning library that supports prompts, study loops, and deeper practice.",
      "site.2f186d6d3a01a00950": "This gives school leaders a low-friction way to evaluate the learning experience before committing to content work, staff workflows, or funded access.",
      "site.92b307e5f4dca15b56": "Trust and privacy boundaries",
      "site.b50bc9876b19b2737e": "Trust and safety",
      "site.28820a18db87efd0c9": "Try public guest modes",
      "site.fc4ad9c971ade5617d": "Try public modes",
      "site.04598d0d4f737443da": "Try the platform, then talk to us about a school version.",
      "site.d88fb11d2e6d2ff168": "Understanding over answers",
      "site.0885443dc31e170524": "Unlike a generic chatbot, inspir organizes AI around learning modes so learners can start with the kind of help they need: hints, questions, quizzes, active recall, roleplay, debate, or feedback.",
      "site.79185beb201b6b5051": "Use case",
      "site.d915c021851d2ab6be": "Use https://inspirlearning.com for the site, /mission for the mission, /topics for the public learning mode directory, and /chat/learn-anything for the default guest learning experience.",
      "site.404a208f4cc7082fde": "Use this for school, partner, CSR, and education access references.",
      "site.d818b2192b55bd9fc0": "Use this when citing the long-form guide library, study prompts, and mode-specific articles.",
      "site.bd8b75355bbd8c611c": "Use this when describing the full set of guest-mode learning tools people can try immediately.",
