      "site.1a1cf3c6d5b17b8a3f": "The best homework help reduces friction without removing the student's responsibility to reason, explain, and revise.",
      "site.c624880a3c3c2d1730": "The better use is feedback, structure, evidence checks, and revision coaching. You can ask it to preserve your voice and avoid replacing the work.",
      "site.9f48b043be28768ae7": "The coding route connects code tutoring, project coaching, data interpretation, research, and concept mapping so learning happens through small testable steps.",
      "site.5a53b3cfc2daf7a31c": "The exam route links planning, quizzes, flashcards, spaced review, and motivation so learners do not confuse rereading with readiness.",
      "site.f00587b6d3ec921cce": "The goal is to make the first click useful: name the subject, choose the right mode, and keep practising.",
      "site.fb6db6b2a3c1a5b24d": "The history route gives learners the liveliness of role-play and debate while preserving the warning that simulations are not primary sources.",
      "site.e769b2568e20189fbf": "The homework route makes the contract visible: ask for a hint, check a step, improve a draft, critique a source, then prove the learning with review.",
      "site.a66eb4fd42f5a5efb6": "The Math Step Coach is built for step checks, hints, and reasoning. It is most useful when you share what you tried and ask it to help you understand the next step.",
      "site.2406c4396ae7f8573a": "The questions this page helps learners answer.",
      "site.355b08a473325b0ac8": "The subject hub links directly to focused chat entrypoints such as Math Step Coach and Writing Coach.",
      "site.7339806b70a3583893": "The subject questions this hub helps with.",
      "site.42adda08bcbc755cd0": "The writing route keeps feedback specific. It favors revision priorities, explain-back, reading comprehension, source checks, and speaking practice over a full rewrite.",
      "site.1d269216797258d100": "These are live guest entrypoints anyone can try. Private learner conversations stay private and are not treated as public learning material.",
      "site.b80976f6f12f3289e7": "These common starting points help learners choose a mode, ask a better question, and leave with a useful next step.",
      "site.e9026b414be20cf906": "These steps make the AI session feel more like tutoring and less like passive answer collection.",
