      "site.89e2c48026f1572f05": "The journey stays anchored in state and evidence: what is known, what is reconstructed, what is speculative, and what your identity can realistically access.",
      "site.b4880449e04d00f78a": "The mode designs vivid locations, paths, and retrieval cues instead of asking you to reread notes.",
