      "site.0470f1fc951f113fe7": "That focus matters. A general chatbot can answer almost anything, but a learning mode gives the conversation a shape. It nudges you toward the kind of thinking, practice, feedback, or exploration that helps the idea stick.",
      "site.7330955fa80ccf7a2f": "This is the same habit behind studying with AI without cheating yourself: keep the learner active. AI is most useful when it gives you feedback on your thinking.",
      "site.171a3417d8d145eb71": "This mode is especially useful for learners who want to:",
      "site.4d25c882fadb2384d9": "This mode is tuned for explain my answer with its own prompts, examples, and learning flow.",
