      "site.2efa1e7572ca417851": "Foundations",
      "site.797fdec6173bdf1a9b": "Get examples at your level.",
      "site.a47c353d55869e468a": "Instead of dropping a long answer, inspir helps you choose a simpler foundation, a deeper route, or a practical example.",
      "site.c7c9ff97842b1e33ba": "Learn Anything",
      "site.48d0a6916b6c7e9da0": "Learn Anything With a Free AI Tutor is a focused way to use AI for learning instead of passive answer collection. The mode is built around a specific job: Curious about absolutely anything? Ask, explore, and go deeper at your pace. Your buddy makes ideas practical, memorable, and easy to build on. Try: \"Explain how the stock market actually works.\"",
      "site.2454155c3547f259bb": "Learn Anything With a Free AI Tutor: practical guide",
      "site.ec8fb13610fbf4e0bb": "Leave with a useful next question.",
      "site.e6f5db8a4f933a2b88": "Prompts to try",
      "site.3ab6679f5e3caafce7": "Start the live mode at Learn Anything. If you want a neighboring learning format, try Socratic Instruction. For a broader view of the platform, read what an AI learning companion should do for everyone.",
