      "site.06220ee349c07fc1d9": "The best learning sessions are adjustable. Cards ask one thing at a time and include traps so review builds understanding, not just recognition.",
      "site.0f19d08b8582e21ef5": "The fastest way to get value from Flashcard Builder is to give the AI a learning job, not just a topic. A topic says what you are interested in. A learning job says what kind of help you need.",
