      "site.725c328ba96c60fa28": "Start with one clear request",
      "site.7b1511f40db7799020": "State the goal in one sentence.",
      "site.1115e8dcfc987db693": "study skills",
      "site.e85f78644fc8f2af1a": "That final recap is important. When you explain the idea back, you reveal what is solid and what is still borrowed from the AI.",
      "site.b717c1703a0a1aaa1e": "The best learning sessions are adjustable. This mode is tuned for geography explorer with its own prompts, examples, and learning flow.",
      "site.c6799bc50adc22a8b9": "The fastest way to get value from Geography Explorer is to give the AI a learning job, not just a topic. A topic says what you are interested in. A learning job says what kind of help you need.",
      "site.eb51e27d05cde20872": "Then add a constraint that makes the session more personal:",
      "site.2e70d2b0915c157e36": "Try one of these starters:",
      "site.fda025881ab1d825c7": "Turn the mode into practice",
      "site.f52be16701e83ab73b": "Use Geography Explorer when this is the right mode for the job. If you want a related path, try Ethics Dilemmas. You can also browse the AI learning blog for study methods, Socratic learning, flashcards, roleplay, and active recall."
