      "site.fbd0875be91d12ed1f": "\"Ask me questions before explaining too much.\"",
      "site.2c2a82b4f1cdf0977f": "\"Check my answer before giving yours.\"",
      "site.f41d6a56bf9f66e73a": "\"Check my essay thesis\"",
      "site.6e260fa2bd0be72927": "\"Give me a harder version after I try.\"",
      "site.ae851fff68c130fe90": "\"Give me a hint for this physics problem\"",
      "site.fd2156a47f3ce6d24a": "\"Help me start this word problem\"",
      "site.4d7d2a10206673f8d7": "\"Keep it beginner friendly.\"",
      "site.f220c4da97503ce8a6": "\"Use examples from my exam, project, or daily life.\"",
      "site.c07cedd8f400fab1d3": "AI prompts",
      "site.3334a6e430d61212aa": "Ask for a tiny first task.",
      "site.c7ade179f07b420526": "End with a recap you write yourself.",
      "site.327c6c47082f6e0457": "For Homework Coach, a useful practice loop is:",
