      "site.fda025881ab1d825c7": "Turn the mode into practice",
      "site.0843ee02d48520170f": "Use Talk to a historical person when this is the right mode for the job. If you want a related path, try Time travel. You can also browse the AI learning blog for study methods, Socratic learning, flashcards, roleplay, and active recall."
